data.description: The property is a charming townhouse located in the heart of Baltimore, MD. This beautiful home was constructed in 2005 and boasts a well-designed layout spread across three stories. With a total finished area of approximately 2,230 square feet, this property offers ample space for comfortable living and entertaining.As you enter the townhouse, you are greeted by a cozy foyer that leads you into a nice FR. Just up one level is the  main living area. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, sitting area, dining area, kitchen, and bright sunroom creating a seamless flow between the spaces. The living room provides a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. The large windows flood the room with natural light, enhancing the overall ambiance.The well-appointed kitchen is a highlight of this property. It features modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar. Whether you are a seasoned chef or enjoy cooking as a hobby, this kitchen provides everything you need to create delicious meals for your members and friends.Property  offers two full bathrooms and one half bathroom, ensuring that everyone's needs are met. These bathrooms are tastefully designed and feature high-quality fixtures, adding a touch of luxury to everyday routines. The bedrooms are spacious and offer comfortable retreats for rest and relaxation. Each room is thoughtfully designed, with ample closet space and large windows that allow for plenty of natural light. The master bedroom comes with it's own full bathroom which includes a huge soaking tub and shower. There is also a den off of the master bedroom which leads to the second balcony. The den could be used as a sitting room or office. One of the standout features of this property is its lot size, which spans approximately 1,133 square feet. Although this may not be a large outdoor space, this home boasts two nice sized balconies, allowing you to enjoy the outdoors without the burden of extensive maintenance. Whether relaxing on your balcony off the master bedroom or having a glass of ice tea on your balcony off the sunroom on the main level, you will always be able to take in a breath of fresh air. The property also comes with a two car garage and two car carport. Therefore,  you will never have to worry about parking for you and your guests.The location of this property is another point of appeal. Situated in Baltimore, MD, it offers easy access to various amenities and attractions. This townhouse is surrounded by popular areas such as, Little Italy, Inner Harbor, Harbor East, and Fells Point, just to name a few. Whether you want to explore local shops and restaurants or take advantage of the city's vibrant cultural scene, you will find everything you need just a short distance away. Additionally, the townhouse is conveniently located near major transportation routes, making commuting a breeze.In summary, property is a beautiful townhouse built in 2005 in Baltimore, MD. With its spacious layout, modern amenities, and attractive features, it offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle. Whether you are a first-time homeowner, or growing household, this property provides the perfect combination of style, functionality, and location. Don't miss the opportunity to make this townhouse your new home.
